CHICKEN PARM SPAGHETTI PIE

INGREDIENTS
* 	2 chicken breasts, butterflied
* 	Salt & pepper, to season
* 	100g flour
* 	4 eggs, beaten
* 	180g panko breadcrumbs
* 	1 ltr vegetable oil, for frying
* 	800g spaghetti
* 	150g parmesan
* 	5 eggs
* 	250ml double cream
* 	1 tbsp salt
* 	1/2 tbsp black pepper
* 	Sliced mozzarella
* 	1 tablespoon olive oil
* 	1 large onion chopped
* 	2 teaspoons minced garlic
* 	400g tomato passata
* 	Salt and pepper to taste
* 	1 teaspoon dried Italian herbs
* 	1 teaspoon sugar

SERVES
6 people
INGREDIENTS
Beef Stew:
2 tbsp flour
Salt and pepper
1 lb diced stewing beef
1 tbsp vegetable oil
1 tbsp butter
2 onions, diced small
500g mushrooms, sliced
2 cloves garlic, diced small
2 tbsp flour
1 tbsp tomato paste
2 cups red wine
1 1/2 cups beef stock
1 tsp salt
1 tsp pepper
 
Calzone Dough:
½ cup warm water
.25oz dry yeast
1 tsp yeast
½ cup water
2 tbsp olive oil
2 tbsp honey
¼ tsp salt
3 cups plain flour
 
Grated Cheddar Cheese
 
Garlic Butter:
½ cup salted butter
3 cloves garlic, minced
1 tbsp Chopped parsley
Pepper

Beef Birra Dough Ball Dip Tray

INGREDIENTS
Birria 
* 	5 dried guajillo, deseeded and halved
* 	8 meaty beef ribs
* 	1 tablespoon flaked sea salt
* 	¼ cup neutral oil, such as canola or grapeseed
* 	1 medium white onion, finely chopped
* 	400g. chopped tomatoes
* 	2 poblano chiles from a jar 
* 	6 garlic cloves, peeled
* 	2 tablespoons finely grated fresh ginger
* 	2 teaspoons dried oregano
* 	2 teaspoons toasted white sesame seeds
* 	½ teaspoon ground cumin
* 	4 cloves
*  Fresh black pepper
* 	1 cinnamon stick
* 	2 bay leaves
* 	Lime juice, to taste
Milk Buns
* 	240 ml whole milk, lukewarm 
* 	2 tsp fast action, dry yeast 
* 	1 tbsp sugar 
* 	2 large egg, whisked 
* 	1 ½ tsp salt
* 	500g bread flour 
* 	80g soft butter 
Salsa
* 	1 small red onion, finely chopped
* 	6 or so small tomatoes, finely chopped
* 	Handful coriander, finely chopped
* 	1 lime, juiced
* 	1 small jalapeno chilli, finely chopped

INGREDIENTS
* 	5 small chicken breasts, butterflied
* 	2 cups plain flour

* 	2 cups golden breadcrumbs
* 	oil, for frying
* 	2 cups tomato sauce
* 	1 cup barbeque sauce
* 	2 cups cream cheese
* 	1/4 cup milk
* 	1 cup parmesan, grated
* 	1 tsp salt
* 	1 tsp black pepper
* 	12 lasagna sheets
* 	2 cups crispy bacon
* 	mozzarella, sliced
* 	red leicester, sliced
